name: ExtensionDataRequirement_CodeFilter
title: Cross-version Extension `R5.DataRequirement.codeFilter` for use in FHIR R4
description: This cross-version extension represents the FHIR R5 element `DataRequirement.codeFilter` for use in FHIR R4.
purpose:
This extension is part of the cross-version definitions generated to enable use of the
element `DataRequirement.codeFilter` as defined in FHIR R5
in FHIR R4.

The source element is defined as:
`DataRequirement.codeFilter` 0..* `Element`

Across FHIR versions, the element set has been mapped as:
*  R5: `DataRequirement.codeFilter` 0..* `Element`
*  R4B: `DataRequirement.codeFilter` 0..* `Element`
*  R4: `DataRequirement.codeFilter` 0..* `Element`

Following are the generation technical comments:
Element `DataRequirement.codeFilter` has is mapped to FHIR R4 element `DataRequirement.codeFilter`, but has no comparisons.
